{"tid":1381412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚共產黨而又不停話香港人港獨既藍屍","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:37:51.000Z","uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0efbd276b082b144cace33edbcb0b6ad88164fe","tid":1381412,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"同佢地講 港獨起因係一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n依加全港市民會一齊要求一國一制<br />\n<br />\n立即取消香港特別行政區 <br />\n<br />\n所有野立即跟曬所有大陸規條<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人好撚想即刻跟番大陸個套 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我好撚愛中國</span></span><br />\n<br />\n問佢願唔願意支持 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔支持 <br />\n<br />\n其實班藍屍先係真港獨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n支持咪攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf23e364cd27fe3f1ef70b027e104842f92321b2","tid":1381412,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}